## Project Structure
```
ctk_colorpicker_plus/
    __init__.py
    ctk_color_picker.py          # Modal dialog
    ctk_color_picker_widget.py   # Embeddable widget
    color_utils.py               # Shared color math and helpers
    color_wheel.png
    target.png
examples/
    demo.py
```

